OL,3,CIran's Strait of Hormuz warning casts
OL,4,Cdoubt on UK-France defensive mission
OL,6,FMine clearance in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,7,Fwill only be carried out by Iran, the
OL,8,Fregime has said, casting doubt on a
OL,9,Fplanned UK and French-led mission to
OL,10,Fmake the vital oil supply route safe
OL,11,Ffor shipping.
OL,13,FThe country's deputy foreign minister,
OL,14,FKazem Gharibabadi, said this was in
OL,15,Fline with the interim ceasefire deal
OL,16,Fsigned with the US as Tehran moved to
OL,17,Fmaintain its grip on the strategic
OL,18,Fwaterway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
