OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782778699
OL,3,CIran's Strait of Hormuz warning casts
OL,4,Cdoubt on UK-France defensive mission
OL,6,FHis remarks came in response to French
OL,7,FPresident Emmanuel Macron, who said
OL,8,Fhis country would work with Oman "in
OL,9,Fco-ordination with our partners" to
OL,10,Fdemine the Gulf channel and ensure
OL,11,Ffree passage for vessels.
OL,13,FBritain and France have been at the
OL,14,Fforefront of a proposed international
OL,15,Fmission to protect and reassure
OL,16,Fvessels using the strait once
OL,17,Fhostilities are over.
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
