OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782778699
OL,3,CIran's Strait of Hormuz warning casts
OL,4,Cdoubt on UK-France defensive mission
OL,6,FEnding Tehran's stranglehold on the
OL,7,Fstrategic waterway, which disrupted
OL,8,Fglobal oil and gas supplies and drove
OL,9,Fup fuel and food prices, had been a
OL,10,Fkey demand in negotiations.
OL,12,FHowever, the sea route remains a
OL,13,Fflashpoint for the fragile truce, with
OL,14,Fan attack on a cargo ship sparking a
OL,15,Ffour-day exchange of fire between the
OL,16,Ftwo sides that threatened the
OL,17,Fagreement aimed at ending the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
