OL,3,CIran's Strait of Hormuz warning casts
OL,4,Cdoubt on UK-France defensive mission
OL,6,FMeanwhile, after trading strikes over
OL,7,Fthe weekend and with an apparent pause
OL,8,Fin attacks, the US is sending a high-
OL,9,Flevel delegation to Qatar to hold
OL,10,Ftalks with Iran, although Tehran has
OL,11,Fdenied a meeting is happening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
